title: Avon Anew Genics Eye Treatment 0.5 oz
L'Oreal Paris Revitalift Miracle Blur Cream, Oil-Free, 1.18 Fluid Ounce
description: Now in an oil-free, non-SPF formula, Miracle Blur Oil-Free is an Instant Skin Smoother that instantly erases the look of lines, wrinkles and pores. Its innovative lightweight texture is translucent to blend seamlessly into skin for a clean, silky-smooth finish. What Is Miracle Blur? It's NOT a moisturizer, NOT a foundation, MORE than a primer; it's the first of-its-kind Instant Skin Smoother. Now in an oil-free formula! What Does It Do? Miracle Blur Oil-Free instantly erases the look of lines, wrinkles, and pores. When Should I Use It? Apply after moisturizer and blend evenly into skin. Wear alone or under foundation. Use all over face, or squeeze a smaller amount for targeted application. Ideal for all skin types. Suggested Skincare Regimen: STEP 1: TREAT *Suggested products: Triple Power Concentrated Serum, Triple Power Eye Treatment STEP 2: MOISTURIZE *Suggested products: Triple Power Deep-Acting Moisturizer STEP 3: FINISH Miracle Blur Oil-Free
